opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 20th day of January, 2010, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus and the Application for an Evidentiary Hearing are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
